SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

2022-03-18 18:47:20.429 +03:30 [INF] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

2022-03-18 19:20:05.222 +03:30 [INF] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

SELECT [p].[CreateOn], [p].[UpdateOn], [p].[PublishDate], [p].[ID], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Price], [p].[Sku], [p].[StockQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
FROM [Product] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Name], [p0].[CategoryID], [p0].[ProductID], [c].[ID]
    FROM [ProductCategory] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]

    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p0].[CategoryID] = [c].[ID]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ID] = [t].[ProductID]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p1] ON [p].[ID] = [p1].[ProductID]
WHERE ([p].[Deleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([p].[StockQuantity] <= 0)
ORDER BY [p].[ID], [t].[CategoryID], [t].[ProductID], [t].[ID], [p1].[CategoryID], [p1].[ProductID]
